name: unparalleled
description:
This is a great little game.

The circle will continue to move forward, and you need to continuously click the left mouse button to control the height of the circle.
The horizontal line in the middle is irregular.
Your task is to control the height of the circle!
When the circle touches the horizontal line, the game will fail!
The operation of this game is very simple, and players will feel very relaxed when playing against a charming solid color background.
1. High definition cartoon
2. Interesting Games

3. The tense and exciting game process

This is an interesting game that players of all ages can easily play.
